# Ranking in Hive

1.Rank
2.Dense Rank
3.Row Number
4.Partition By

# Let us first create the table and load the data

Note: we will be considering rank_dataset.csv as our dataset for practicals

[cloudera@quickstart Downloads]$ cat rank_dataset.csv
John,1500
Albert,1500
Mark,1000
Frank,1150
Loopa,1100
